full_text: Speaking of Jimmy G, let's check QBs EPA rankings after correcting for YAC over expected. Garoppolo has the most EPA generated by his WRs, however, he is still 7th in EPA when accounting for this. Other QBs getting helped by YAC o/e are Mahomes (-8) and Burrow (-8). #nflverse https://t.co/ERHkwjEDOt
